    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📋 Daily Gmail Digest Workflow\n\n**Purpose:** Fetch all unread Gmail emails from the last 24 hours, summarize each with Google Gemini, and post a formatted digest to Slack.\n\n**Schedule:** Every day at 8:00 AM\n\n**Slack Channel:** `#daily-email-digest`\n\n---\n\n### Input Schema\n| Field | Type | Source |\n|-------|------|--------|\n| subject | string | Gmail |\n| body (textPlain) | string | Gmail |\n| from | string | Gmail |\n| date | ISO datetime | Gmail |\n| isUnread | boolean | Gmail filter |\n\n### Output Format\n`• [Subject] (from: Sender): [1-2 sentence Gemini summary]`",
        "height": 350,
        "width": 400
      },
      "id": "3037d3fa-7b69-4153-afc8-4b6728243bbc",
      "name": "Sticky Note - Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ⚠️ Error Handling\n\n**Gmail failure →** Posts error to Slack, marks workflow failed.\n\n**No emails →** Posts \"No unread emails\" to Slack, marks complete.\n\n**Gemini failure →** Retries once (3s delay). If still fails, uses fallback text and continues so other emails aren't blocked.\n\n**Slack failure →** Workflow errors visibly in n8n execution log.",
        "height": 250,
        "width": 350
      },
      "id": "03bb6604-3433-4345-b83b-7bf75e341630",
      "name": "Sticky Note - Error Handling",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        32,
        416
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
       "url": "https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-2.5-flash:generateContent?key=YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"contents\": [\n    {\n      \"parts\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \"Summarize this email in 1-2 concise sentences. Focus on key action items. No preamble.\\n\\nSubject: {{ $json.subject }}\\nFrom: {{ $json.from }}\\nBody: {{ $json.body }}\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.4,
      "position": [
        1472,
        256
      ],
      "id": "34e75820-cfbf-4867-9a4f-f3677a2f088c",
      "name": "Summarize Email with Gemini",
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 5000,
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput"
    },
    {
